00:51:02.601 --> 00:51:04.600
And it's great to just
get your voice out there,

00:51:04.600 --> 00:51:06.809
but then you also
don't want to lose

00:51:06.809 --> 00:51:08.734
that proper English
language over time.

00:51:08.734 --> 00:51:10.150
KATE KERRIGAN: But
